---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy"
  description="How Tutelare handles personal information submitted through the site."
>
  <h1
    class="font-semibold leading-tight mb-6"
    style="font-family: var(--font-serif); font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 2.75rem)"
  >
    Privacy
  </h1>

  <p class="text-sm" style="color: var(--color-ink-muted)">
    Last updated: <time datetime="2026-05-23">May 23, 2026</time>
  </p>

  <section class="mt-8">
    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3" style="font-family: var(--font-serif)">
      What we collect
    </h2>
    <p>
      Tutelare does not run analytics, tracking pixels, or third-party cookies on this site.
      The only personal information we collect is what you choose to send us — for example,
      a message submitted through a contact form or an email sent to
      <a href="mailto:sthurlow@tutelare.ai">sthurlow@tutelare.ai</a>.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="mt-8">
    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3" style="font-family: var(--font-serif)">
      How we use it
    </h2>
    <p>
      We use the information you provide solely to respond to your message and to follow up
      on potential engagements. We do not sell or share your information with third parties.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="mt-8">
    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3" style="font-family: var(--font-serif)">
      How long we retain it
    </h2>
    <p>
      We retain correspondence for the duration of any active engagement plus a reasonable
      business-record retention period. You can request deletion of your correspondence at
      any time by emailing <a href="mailto:sthurlow@tutelare.ai">sthurlow@tutelare.ai</a>.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="mt-8">
    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3" style="font-family: var(--font-serif)">
      Your rights
    </h2>
    <p>
      If you are located in the European Union, the United Kingdom, California, or any other
      jurisdiction with applicable data protection law, you may have additional rights
      including access, correction, and deletion of your personal information. Contact
      <a href="mailto:sthurlow@tutelare.ai">sthurlow@tutelare.ai</a> to exercise these rights.
    </p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
